type.description:
## Creative Flight

---


[Power Type](https://origins.readthedocs.io/en/latest/types/power_types/creative_flight)

Allows the players to fly as if they were in Creative Mode.

Type ID: `origins:creative_flight`

---

### Examples

```json
{
    "type": "origins:creative_flight"
}
```
